      "text": [
        "120 - وَقَالَ اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ: «اِكْتَحِلُوا وَتْراً وَ اِسْتَاكُوا عَرْضاً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.120 - The Prophet, said: \"Apply kohl in an odd number of strokes and use siwak (tooth cleaning) across the width of the mouth”."
        ]
      }
    }
